{"tid":346393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚世轉會】癲！PSG原來用8億歐元搶尼馬","createTime":"2017-08-04T02:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T23:22:39.000Z","uid":31208,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a9eb110f549d98f6a2b9cccfc6dcaa59be53273","tid":346393,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:13:31.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿官方確認，收到2.22億歐元違約金同尼馬解約，但巴黎聖日耳門成功搶人，實際上付出嘅代價高得多，消息話佢哋畀咗3億歐元尼馬，名義上邀請佢擔任2022年卡塔爾世盃大使，實則畀佢找違約金條數，另外再畀1億歐元簽字費，至氹得掂佢個貪錢老竇。<br />\n<br />\n咁都未止，PSG為尼馬提供除稅前嘅8,000萬歐元年薪5年合約，總值4億歐元，換句話聖日耳門狂燒8億歐元，等於74億港紙先至能夠完成轉會。星期五香港嘅六合彩頭獎彩金高達5,600萬港元，都要中132次至買得起尼馬，問你怕未！"},{"pid":"0a947b58c82c5233997f43de2f0b2fe770e16b67","tid":346393,"uid":37735,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"班中東友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無限金錢一樣野<br />\n<br />\n擾亂世界金融<br />\n金援恐怖分子"},{"pid":"8cbdbce7e58a602689cbbade329d37c32384767d","tid":346393,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3a58601d36f4cf188c074f6bc1f4975944358b8","tid":346393,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n幾倍普巴<br />\n今季曼聯買返丙朗又要再俾多啲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eede0490bbc2d062171571935b0b986c33d2b26","tid":346393,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:36:16.000Z","msg":"尼馬都好少少，佢個仆街貪錢廢柴老豆真係好黑人憎"},{"pid":"d979a9807aa994d0938849d535da6f4064a66b00","tid":346393,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"報警<br />\n<br />\n星期五六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e2311fe51b2c4aa19b84e1c787fce6c17362aa","tid":346393,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T02:53